<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
      <div class="profile-card p-4 p-md-5">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="mv-icon-wrap m-0">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-file-contract"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h1 class="fw-bold mb-0" style="font-size: 2rem; color: var(--nm-text);">Terms of Service</h1>
            <p class="text-muted mb-0" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Last updated: July 2026</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="lead text-muted mb-4" style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75;">
          By accessing or using the Neuro_Mentor platform, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following Terms & Conditions. Please read them carefully.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-4" style="border-color: var(--nm-border-light);">

        <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--nm-text); font-size: 1.25rem;">1. Platform Purpose</h4>
            <p class="text-muted" style="line-height: 1.7;">
              Neuro_Mentor is a marketplace that connects independent student/professional mentors with students seeking specific concept clearing. We do not provide academic degrees or guarantee specific grades in institutional examinations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--nm-text); font-size: 1.25rem;">2. User Conduct & Accounts</h4>
            <ul class="text-muted ps-3 d-flex flex-column gap-2" style="line-height: 1.7;">
              <li>You must provide accurate credentials and profile information during registration.</li>
              <li>Seniors and professionals register as independent educators and are responsible for the quality of tutoring they offer.</li>
              <li>Academic dishonesty, cheating, or completing exams on behalf of a student is strictly prohibited on this platform.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--nm-text); font-size: 1.25rem;">3. Hourly Billing & Wallet</h4>
            <p class="text-muted" style="line-height: 1.7;">
              Educators set their own rates on an hourly basis. Students load funds to their wallet balance to facilitate hourly session bookings. Platform transaction issues can be reported directly to support for resolution.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--nm-text); font-size: 1.25rem;">4. Limitation of Liability</h4>
            <p class="text-muted" style="line-height: 1.7;">
              Neuro_Mentor is not liable for disputes arising directly out of communication or tutoring quality between educators and students. We reserve the right to ban users who violate code of conduct.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-5 text-center">
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-4">Back to Home</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
